24
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:30,319
and healthy.

25
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,680
This is the most expensive meal we offer here.

26
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:33,759
Although

27
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:34,879
they are simple,

28
