00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:08,960
Maybe you're not meant to take the exam.

301
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,759
Just accept it.

302
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,919
You're a girl.

303
00:11:12,279 --> 00:11:14,279
Stop having an unrealistic dream.

304
00:11:14,279 --> 00:11:14,919
You'll wear yourself out.

305
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,519
You have earned good money anyway.

306
00:11:17,759 --> 00:11:19,200
Find a good husband.

307
00:11:19,559 --> 00:11:20,440
That's your priority.

308
00:11:22,559 --> 00:11:23,720
Didn't you say

309
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:24,440
that you

310
00:11:24,559 --> 00:11:25,879
couldn't register online

311
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,279
so you would check on-site?

312
00:11:27,279 --> 00:11:28,279
So what happened?

313
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,480
I checked with my ID number

314
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,639
but it said duplicate registration.

315
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,480
I couldn't register back then

316
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:37,759
and now, the system

317
00:11:37,759 --> 00:11:39,200
doesn't have my registration record.

318
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,039
Duplicate registration?

319
00:11:41,279 --> 00:11:41,919
See?

320
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:42,799
Xiuyu,

321
00:11:42,799 --> 00:11:43,799
I'll be frank.

322
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,559
You're careless

323
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:47,120
so you must have messed up somewhere.

324
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:51,759
It's like your National College Entrance Exam.

325
00:11:52,679 --> 00:11:53,879
You thought you aced it

326
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:54,480
but...

327
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:00,720
Perhaps

328
00:12:00,919 --> 00:12:02,120
we can ask Qingzhi?

329
00:12:02,559 --> 00:12:03,799
He works for the government

330
00:12:04,159 --> 00:12:05,039
so he can ask around.

331
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,159
Exactly.

332
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,720
That's easy.

333
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:13,200
I have a friend working for the Ministry
of Human Resources and Social Security.

334
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:14,440
I'll ask him to help

335
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,440
when I go to work tomorrow.

336
00:12:18,639 --> 00:12:19,679
Calm down, Xiuyu.

337
00:12:19,879 --> 00:12:20,320
Perhaps

338
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,399
it's a system error.

339
00:12:21,759 --> 00:12:22,759
I'll ask him to check

340
00:12:22,759 --> 00:12:23,759
tomorrow.

341
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:28,080
The rain in the mountain can appear so abruptly.

342
00:12:28,519 --> 00:12:29,879
It's so heavy.

343
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:31,720
Don't worry.

344
00:12:33,039 --> 00:12:34,759
Everything will be prepared.

345
00:12:37,399 --> 00:12:38,200
Sure.

346
00:12:38,519 --> 00:12:39,399
Oh, dear.

347
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:41,559
What a horrible path.

348
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:43,320
It's so muddy.

349
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,039
Mr. Wu.

350
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,879
Where were you?

351
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,759
I was looking for inspiration

352
00:12:48,639 --> 00:12:50,440
but then heavy rain descended on me.

353
00:12:51,559 --> 00:12:52,600
The rain has washed away

354
00:12:52,639 --> 00:12:53,919
all my inspiration.

355
00:12:55,039 --> 00:12:55,440
Come.

356
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,000
Have some water.

357
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:56,919
Thank you.

358
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,360
-Take a rest here.
-Thank you.

359
00:13:01,799 --> 00:13:02,600
Xingfu,

360
00:13:02,679 --> 00:13:03,960
the path becomes dangerous

361
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,200
when it rains.

362
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,919
Many clients have complained about it.

363
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:10,559
We really need to fix it.

364
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,279
Right.

365
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,440
We have to solve this issue

366
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,320
immediately.

367
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:53,440
To the right. To the right.

368
00:13:54,879 --> 00:13:55,559
Miss Chen.

369
00:13:56,759 --> 00:13:57,440
You're here.

370
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:58,919
-This car...
-Let me take a look.

371
00:13:58,919 --> 00:13:59,799
-has sunken into the mud.
-Let me see.

372
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,039
Let me put this underneath it.

373
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:01,639
See if it helps.

374
00:14:01,639 --> 00:14:02,279
Okay.

375
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:02,919
Thank you.

376
00:14:10,799 --> 00:14:11,279
Go.

377
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:12,279
Step...

378
00:14:12,279 --> 00:14:13,039
Step on the gas.

379
00:14:13,039 --> 00:14:13,799
Step on it.

380
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:18,840
Try again.

381
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,000
Hold on.

382
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:22,600
Stop.

383
00:14:22,679 --> 00:14:23,440
Halt.

384
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,279
It won't work.

385
00:14:26,039 --> 00:14:26,720
Careful.

386
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:30,679
It's slippery here.

387
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,720
I'm so sorry.

388
00:14:33,799 --> 00:14:35,240
This is the only muddy road.

389
00:14:35,399 --> 00:14:36,440
It'll be all right in front.

390
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,399
I'm so sorry.

391
00:14:40,279 --> 00:14:41,679
We will fix this road in two days.

392
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,440
Mind the steps.

393
00:14:46,879 --> 00:14:48,080
We're almost there.

394
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:51,026
[Niaofei Creek]
[Xingfu Inn]

395
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:03,960
Liu,

396
00:15:04,759 --> 00:15:05,399
what did you get?

397
00:15:05,639 --> 00:15:06,519
You sounded so urgent

398
00:15:06,519 --> 00:15:07,720
so I thought it was something serious.

399
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:09,240
Your sister is quite harebrained.

400
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:10,399
She has already passed the exam.

401
00:15:10,559 --> 00:15:11,080
Does she

402
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:11,919
want to take it again?

403
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:12,639
What?

404
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:14,440
Why do you sound so surprised?

405
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:15,240
The system says

406
00:15:15,279 --> 00:15:16,840
that she has obtained
the accounting certificate.

407
00:15:16,879 --> 00:15:17,759
It will not be reissued

408
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,120
and that's why she can't register.

409
00:15:19,759 --> 00:15:20,159
All right.

410
00:15:20,159 --> 00:15:21,000
I have to go.

411
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:22,399
I'll download the digital copy

412
00:15:22,399 --> 00:15:23,000
and send it to your mailbox.

413
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:23,799
Check it yourself.

414
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:24,919
Thank you.

415
00:15:44,956 --> 00:15:48,075
[Accounting Certificate,
Wang Xiuyu]

416
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,039
What's going on, Xiuyu?

417
00:15:55,879 --> 00:15:56,440
Xiuyu?

418
00:15:57,159 --> 00:15:57,799
What's going on?

419
00:16:00,159 --> 00:16:01,399
How can this be,

420
00:16:01,399 --> 00:16:02,200
Qingzhi?

421
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,879
Chuanmei got accepted to a university

422
00:16:05,879 --> 00:16:08,039
but I wasn't.

423
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:10,879
Didn't you say you did well?

424
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:13,919
How would I know?

425
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:15,879
I checked the answers.

426
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:17,279
I got

427
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:18,679
many right answers.

428
00:16:18,679 --> 00:16:20,559
Why didn't I pass the exam?

429
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:21,399
It shouldn't be.

430
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:22,200
There, there.

431
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:24,919
Chuanmei passed but I didn't.

432
00:16:25,039 --> 00:16:25,879
There, there.

433
00:16:28,092 --> 00:16:30,725
[Wang Xiuyu, ID card details]

434
00:16:46,620 --> 00:16:47,220
Hey,

435
00:16:47,530 --> 00:16:48,220
I'm Qingzhi.

436
00:16:49,020 --> 00:16:49,930
I need you

437
00:16:50,100 --> 00:16:51,050
to check something for me.

438
00:16:56,570 --> 00:16:57,220
Qingzhi,

439
00:16:58,100 --> 00:16:59,410
what did you find?

440
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:03,570
What?

441
00:17:04,860 --> 00:17:05,810
Chuanmei?

442
00:17:10,260 --> 00:17:11,500
I don't have her number.

443
00:17:12,260 --> 00:17:13,620
Let me call Chuanjia.

444
00:17:14,530 --> 00:17:15,420
Didn't you say

445
00:17:15,420 --> 00:17:16,940
you would fix the road once you get paid?

446
00:17:17,700 --> 00:17:20,050
And didn't Mr. Xie pay you?

447
00:17:20,290 --> 00:17:20,980
Yes,

448
00:17:21,050 --> 00:17:22,530
he did.

449
00:17:23,050 --> 00:17:23,980
But the payment

450
00:17:24,090 --> 00:17:25,700
is barely enough to pay my debt.

451
00:17:25,900 --> 00:17:26,660
Many people

452
00:17:26,900 --> 00:17:29,290
still have to pay up.

453
00:17:29,610 --> 00:17:31,130
Then when will you do this for me?

454
00:17:31,810 --> 00:17:32,420
Give me

455
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:33,220
an answer.

456
00:17:33,290 --> 00:17:35,500
I told you within a month, didn't I?

457
00:17:35,570 --> 00:17:36,900
A month hasn't gone by.

458
00:17:36,900 --> 00:17:38,420
Please understand.

459
00:17:39,020 --> 00:17:40,220
I am understanding.

460
00:17:40,260 --> 00:17:41,420
Am I not understanding enough?

461
00:17:41,420 --> 00:17:42,500
I have been postponing the project.

462
00:17:43,050 --> 00:17:43,810
Approve

463
00:17:43,810 --> 00:17:44,810
it now.

464
00:17:45,050 --> 00:17:45,940
Look outside.

465
00:17:46,420 --> 00:17:47,980
It's rainy season soon.

466
00:17:48,370 --> 00:17:49,050
Muddy path

467
00:17:49,050 --> 00:17:49,810
and rain

468
00:17:49,810 --> 00:17:50,700
are a dangerous combination.

469
00:17:53,530 --> 00:17:54,180
Look.

470
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:56,330
You opened this inn

471
00:17:57,260 --> 00:17:58,810
so that the city people

472
00:17:58,980 --> 00:18:00,660
can experience a slice

473
00:18:00,810 --> 00:18:01,770
of rural life.

474
00:18:01,850 --> 00:18:02,290
Right?

475
00:18:02,740 --> 00:18:04,090
You can tell them

476
00:18:04,290 --> 00:18:05,850
this is part of rural life.

477
00:18:06,420 --> 00:18:07,980
How can I possibly tell them that?

478
00:18:08,980 --> 00:18:09,810
Only you...

479
00:18:09,810 --> 00:18:10,260
I...

480
00:18:12,130 --> 00:18:13,660
[Xiuyu]
You want them to come all the way here

481
00:18:13,700 --> 00:18:14,850
just to trudge

482
00:18:14,850 --> 00:18:15,850
in the mud?

483
00:18:16,530 --> 00:18:17,570
Let me take this call first.

484
00:18:20,770 --> 00:18:21,330
Hello?

485
00:18:23,180 --> 00:18:23,900
Chuanmei?

486
00:18:23,900 --> 00:18:24,740
She does have

487
00:18:24,740 --> 00:18:25,610
a new phone number now.

488
00:18:26,260 --> 00:18:27,020
Are you looking for her?

489
00:18:31,850 --> 00:18:33,130
I'm not sure about that.

490
00:18:34,050 --> 00:18:34,530
You know what?

491
00:18:34,810 --> 00:18:36,900
I'll contact her for you.

492
00:18:36,900 --> 00:18:37,740
I'll get back to you soon.

493
00:18:37,740 --> 00:18:38,220
All right?

494
00:18:40,500 --> 00:18:41,050
Okay.

495
00:18:53,610 --> 00:18:54,660
The rainy season is around the corner.

496
00:18:55,260 --> 00:18:55,900
I think

497
00:18:56,740 --> 00:18:58,500
for your inn,

498
00:18:58,570 --> 00:18:59,850
the road construction

499
00:19:01,460 --> 00:19:02,180
is a priority.

500
00:19:09,420 --> 00:19:10,260
I approved it.

501
00:19:10,260 --> 00:19:11,330
Any other problems you wish to solve?

502
00:19:15,530 --> 00:19:16,020
I guess

503
00:19:16,020 --> 00:19:16,700
there's no longer a problem.

504
00:19:17,660 --> 00:19:18,220
All right.

505
00:19:18,220 --> 00:19:19,420
Let me know

506
00:19:19,420 --> 00:19:20,260
if you have any problems.

507
00:19:22,290 --> 00:19:22,810
Okay.

508
00:19:24,850 --> 00:19:25,770
Thanks, Mr. Wan.

509
00:19:26,050 --> 00:19:26,770
I'll leave you be.

510
00:19:26,980 --> 00:19:27,570
Bye.

511
00:19:28,180 --> 00:19:28,700
Xingfu.

512
00:19:32,020 --> 00:19:32,570
Nothing.

513
00:19:58,610 --> 00:19:59,290
Chuanmei,

514
00:20:01,850 --> 00:20:03,260
Xiuyu knows about it now.

515
00:20:04,180 --> 00:20:04,850
I can't hide it any longer.

516
00:20:05,130 --> 00:20:05,740
Come back.

517
00:20:28,420 --> 00:20:29,090
How are you feeling?

518
00:20:29,260 --> 00:20:29,900
Are you tired?

519
00:20:32,810 --> 00:20:33,530
Chuanjia,

520
00:20:34,770 --> 00:20:35,940
have you told dad?

521
00:20:38,370 --> 00:20:39,130
Not yet.

522
00:20:44,700 --> 00:20:45,740
What should I do then?

523
00:20:51,180 --> 00:20:51,940
Don't worry.

524
00:20:52,740 --> 00:20:53,420
I'm here.

525
00:20:55,500 --> 00:20:56,290
Let's go back first.

526
00:20:56,660 --> 00:20:57,370
We'll talk back home.

527
00:21:24,850 --> 00:21:25,740
No way.

528
00:21:44,530 --> 00:21:45,180
Xiuyu,

529
00:21:45,370 --> 00:21:46,220
why are you carrying a cleaver?

530
00:21:46,220 --> 00:21:46,770
Oh, no.

531
00:21:47,290 --> 00:21:47,740
My child.

532
00:21:47,980 --> 00:21:48,770
Don't touch me!

533
00:21:48,770 --> 00:21:49,260
What's the matter?

534
00:21:49,260 --> 00:21:50,940
Come at me! Come at me!

535
00:21:51,220 --> 00:21:52,290
What's going on?

536
00:21:52,420 --> 00:21:53,020
Why?

537
00:21:53,370 --> 00:21:54,500
They have no right.

538
00:21:54,500 --> 00:21:55,850
Absolutely no right!

539
00:21:56,500 --> 00:21:57,460
How can this be?

540
00:21:57,740 --> 00:21:58,370
What happened?

541
00:21:58,370 --> 00:21:59,290
Who took advantage of you?

542
00:21:59,770 --> 00:22:00,260
Tell us.

543
00:22:00,260 --> 00:22:01,700
I checked the answers afterward.

544
00:22:02,660 --> 00:22:04,290
I aced them.

545
00:22:04,530 --> 00:22:05,370
What?

546
00:22:05,370 --> 00:22:06,370
What answers?

547
00:22:06,370 --> 00:22:07,130
Tell us.

548
00:22:07,290 --> 00:22:08,460
Explain, my dear. What happened?

549
00:22:08,460 --> 00:22:09,570
-Speak slowly.
-When she came out,

550
00:22:09,570 --> 00:22:10,700
I even consoled her.

551
00:22:10,700 --> 00:22:11,660
Who?

552
00:22:11,660 --> 00:22:12,770
What are you on about?

553
00:22:12,770 --> 00:22:13,460
Calm down. Don't...

554
00:22:13,460 --> 00:22:14,130
All this time, you were pretending.

555
00:22:14,420 --> 00:22:15,370
Ten years.

556
00:22:15,940 --> 00:22:16,900
For ten years,

557
00:22:16,900 --> 00:22:18,570
I couldn't get over it.

558
00:22:19,370 --> 00:22:20,260
What, my child?

559
00:22:20,260 --> 00:22:21,290
Can you please explain it more clearly?

560
00:22:21,290 --> 00:22:24,220
I felt guilty.

561
00:22:24,220 --> 00:22:27,260
I thought I was a disgrace.

562
00:22:27,500 --> 00:22:28,810
-Who?
-Who exactly are you talking about?

563
00:22:29,660 --> 00:22:30,500
Why?

564
00:22:32,260 --> 00:22:32,660
What happened?

565
00:22:32,660 --> 00:22:33,610
Don't cry, my child.

566
00:22:33,900 --> 00:22:35,050
-Tell us what happened?
-Tell us.

567
00:22:35,610 --> 00:22:36,940
I passed it.

568
00:22:36,940 --> 00:22:37,660
You passed it?

569
00:22:37,660 --> 00:22:38,500
-Passed what?
-What?

570
00:22:38,770 --> 00:22:40,020
I passed it.

571
00:22:40,020 --> 00:22:42,180
Tell us, what exactly is going on?

572
00:22:42,180 --> 00:22:43,740
You mean the accounting certification?

573
00:22:43,740 --> 00:22:44,180
Passed what?

574
00:22:44,180 --> 00:22:45,420
No!

575
00:22:45,420 --> 00:22:46,260
Then what?

576
00:22:46,260 --> 00:22:48,260
I got accepted into a university.

577
00:22:49,940 --> 00:22:51,290
You did?

578
00:22:52,130 --> 00:22:52,810
Wait.

579
00:22:53,090 --> 00:22:54,810
Ten years ago, you failed.

580
00:22:54,810 --> 00:22:55,900
I did pass the exam.

581
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:58,290
But someone took my spot.

582
00:22:59,330 --> 00:23:00,460
Someone took your spot?

583
00:23:00,900 --> 00:23:02,220
-How is that possible?
-Who took your spot?

584
00:23:02,530 --> 00:23:03,330
Who did?

585
00:23:05,660 --> 00:23:06,610
Wan Chuanmei.

586
00:23:06,980 --> 00:23:07,660
Wan...

587
00:23:08,180 --> 00:23:09,700
Wan Chuanmei took my name.

588
00:23:09,700 --> 00:23:10,660
Chuanmei?

589
00:23:11,770 --> 00:23:13,460
So many people got accepted.

590
00:23:13,460 --> 00:23:15,460
Why did she have to take your name?

591
00:23:15,460 --> 00:23:16,810
How am I supposed to know?

592
00:23:16,980 --> 00:23:19,020
She just had to take my name.

593
00:23:19,460 --> 00:23:20,770
She did it

594
00:23:20,770 --> 00:23:22,130
because we aren't an established family here.

595
00:23:22,460 --> 00:23:24,610
Because our surname is Wang and not Wan here.

596
00:23:24,850 --> 00:23:26,290
This is outrageous.

