00:23:26,290 --> 00:23:27,370
Unacceptable.

598
00:23:27,370 --> 00:23:28,610
Are you telling the truth?

599
00:23:29,220 --> 00:23:30,610
Why would I lie to you?

600
00:23:30,740 --> 00:23:31,570
Qingzhi

601
00:23:31,570 --> 00:23:33,660
told me everything.

602
00:23:35,980 --> 00:23:37,020
I'm done with this.

603
00:23:37,180 --> 00:23:38,570
I will fight them with my life.

604
00:23:39,290 --> 00:23:40,500
Dear.

605
00:23:41,370 --> 00:23:42,020
Xiuyu.

606
00:23:43,020 --> 00:23:44,500
Wan Chuanmei,

607
00:23:45,130 --> 00:23:46,810
you're cruel!

608
00:23:46,810 --> 00:23:48,090
Oh, why did this happen?

609
00:23:48,850 --> 00:23:50,770
Why do they always do this to us?

610
00:23:50,770 --> 00:23:51,700
This is serious.

611
00:23:51,700 --> 00:23:53,500
It's about her life.

612
00:23:54,090 --> 00:23:55,940
Why our family?

613
00:23:55,940 --> 00:23:57,740
If you're not good enough, don't go to university.

614
00:23:57,740 --> 00:24:00,460
Why take Xiuyu's spot?

615
00:24:01,740 --> 00:24:03,290
Oh, Xiuyu.

616
00:24:06,660 --> 00:24:08,330
You ruined

617
00:24:08,900 --> 00:24:10,810
my daughter's life.

618
00:24:13,980 --> 00:24:15,020
So unfair.

619
00:24:15,020 --> 00:24:17,050
This is so unfair.

620
00:24:17,940 --> 00:24:19,260
She should be punished.

621
00:24:19,980 --> 00:24:20,940
Bad karma will arrive.

622
00:24:20,940 --> 00:24:22,180
Why would she do that?

623
00:24:23,900 --> 00:24:25,020
It's all my fault.

624
00:24:25,020 --> 00:24:26,050
I'm meek.

625
00:24:27,050 --> 00:24:28,370
I was bullied

626
00:24:29,050 --> 00:24:31,460
and my children will have to be bullied.

627
00:24:33,180 --> 00:24:33,660
Oh, this painful life.

628
00:24:33,660 --> 00:24:34,500
Dad!

629
00:24:35,050 --> 00:24:36,660
Dad!

630
00:24:37,050 --> 00:24:39,090
Why are you hitting yourself?

631
00:24:39,770 --> 00:24:41,180
I'm useless.

632
00:24:41,330 --> 00:24:42,500
So useless.

633
00:24:43,500 --> 00:24:44,090
Mom.

634
00:24:44,420 --> 00:24:45,660
This is not right.

635
00:24:45,770 --> 00:24:47,090
I'm telling you.

636
00:24:48,290 --> 00:24:50,090
If you do not seek justice for me,

637
00:24:50,530 --> 00:24:51,940
if you do not sort this out,

638
00:24:52,660 --> 00:24:53,290
I...

639
00:24:53,810 --> 00:24:55,090
I'll die today.

640
00:24:55,260 --> 00:24:56,420
I'll die in front of their home.

641
00:24:56,420 --> 00:24:57,570
They have to pay for it.

642
00:24:58,020 --> 00:24:59,570
We are here for you.

643
00:25:00,130 --> 00:25:01,700
It's okay, Xiuyu.

644
00:25:01,700 --> 00:25:02,900
It's not the end of the world.

645
00:25:03,090 --> 00:25:03,850
There, there.

646
00:25:04,050 --> 00:25:05,180
Xiuyu.

647
00:25:05,180 --> 00:25:06,700
Xiuyu, listen to me.

648
00:25:06,980 --> 00:25:08,130
Mom is here.

649
00:25:08,530 --> 00:25:11,290
I will not let this slide.

650
00:25:11,290 --> 00:25:13,050
You hear me?

651
00:25:13,370 --> 00:25:14,570
You hear me?

652
00:25:14,660 --> 00:25:16,050
Call Qinglai now.

653
00:25:16,180 --> 00:25:17,370
-Ask him to come back.
-Okay.

654
00:25:17,460 --> 00:25:18,460
I'll call him.

655
00:25:18,850 --> 00:25:19,810
I'll call him.

656
00:25:20,500 --> 00:25:21,290
It's okay.

657
00:25:21,290 --> 00:25:23,530
We're still alive. We'll sort this out.

658
00:26:10,810 --> 00:26:11,370
Dad.

659
00:26:12,770 --> 00:26:13,330
Eh?

660
00:26:15,180 --> 00:26:15,500
Eh?

661
00:26:16,900 --> 00:26:17,500
Dad.

662
00:26:19,330 --> 00:26:20,660
Chuanmei.

663
00:26:21,980 --> 00:26:23,260
Am I dreaming?

664
00:26:26,370 --> 00:26:27,660
I thought I was dreaming.

665
00:26:28,370 --> 00:26:29,420
Why are you back?

666
00:26:30,570 --> 00:26:31,090
Come.

667
00:26:31,090 --> 00:26:32,090
Sit down.

668
00:26:36,570 --> 00:26:38,330
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

669
00:26:39,290 --> 00:26:40,090
Oh, my.

670
00:26:41,420 --> 00:26:43,130
I'm so happy.

671
00:26:44,180 --> 00:26:45,700
Look at you.

672
00:26:46,290 --> 00:26:48,130
Not bad, you two.

673
00:26:50,500 --> 00:26:51,770
Wonderful.

674
00:26:52,660 --> 00:26:53,660
My baby daughter.

675
00:26:54,220 --> 00:26:55,420
My dear.

676
00:26:56,980 --> 00:26:58,020
-You lost weight.
-Dad.

677
00:26:59,050 --> 00:27:00,130
What happened?

678
00:27:00,130 --> 00:27:01,610
Are you too happy to see me?

679
00:27:01,850 --> 00:27:02,900
It's all right.

680
00:27:03,370 --> 00:27:04,130
It's okay.

681
00:27:04,130 --> 00:27:06,370
Save me, Dad.

682
00:27:09,050 --> 00:27:10,020
What's the matter?

683
00:27:10,570 --> 00:27:11,810
What happened?

684
00:27:13,020 --> 00:27:14,090
Don't cry.

685
00:27:14,090 --> 00:27:14,660
Tell me.

686
00:27:14,660 --> 00:27:15,700
What happened?

687
00:27:16,420 --> 00:27:17,330
What's going on?

688
00:27:17,850 --> 00:27:18,530
There, there.

689
00:27:18,530 --> 00:27:19,130
My child.

690
00:27:19,530 --> 00:27:20,330
Tell me.

691
00:27:20,460 --> 00:27:20,980
Dad.

692
00:27:20,980 --> 00:27:21,770
What happened?

693
00:27:22,180 --> 00:27:23,090
Let me say it.

694
00:27:24,740 --> 00:27:25,770
Don't get too agitated

695
00:27:26,850 --> 00:27:28,090
after you hear what I will say.

696
00:27:28,610 --> 00:27:30,050
The doctor said you

697
00:27:30,050 --> 00:27:31,020
shouldn't be agitated.

698
00:27:31,020 --> 00:27:32,770
Get to the point. What happened?

699
00:27:41,530 --> 00:27:42,610
What are you doing?

700
00:27:45,850 --> 00:27:47,090
Chuanmei

701
00:27:47,980 --> 00:27:49,700
took Xiuyu's slot to attend university.

702
00:27:53,050 --> 00:27:54,050
Back then,

703
00:27:54,500 --> 00:27:55,980
Wang Xiuyu got accepted to the university.

704
00:27:56,740 --> 00:27:57,810
But then the Wangs

705
00:27:58,500 --> 00:28:00,050
kept telling everyone that they hoped

706
00:28:00,330 --> 00:28:01,460
their daughter would never pass.

707
00:28:01,700 --> 00:28:03,570
If she passed, they wouldn't have the money
for the tuition fee.

708
00:28:05,570 --> 00:28:06,700
Chuanmei failed the exam.

709
00:28:11,050 --> 00:28:12,130
When she came home,

710
00:28:13,130 --> 00:28:15,020
she cried for two days straight
without eating or drinking.

711
00:28:15,610 --> 00:28:17,740
As her brother,
I couldn't bear seeing her like that.

712
00:28:18,420 --> 00:28:19,290
You were very occupied

713
00:28:19,290 --> 00:28:20,330
and I couldn't contact you.

714
00:28:21,460 --> 00:28:22,610
Then, I heard

715
00:28:23,460 --> 00:28:25,260
someone knew a way to help

716
00:28:25,530 --> 00:28:27,020
those who failed to get into a university,

717
00:28:27,020 --> 00:28:28,180
as long as there were available spots.

718
00:28:28,290 --> 00:28:29,330
I spent 20,000 yuan on this.

719
00:28:31,700 --> 00:28:34,050
I had a lapse of judgment

720
00:28:35,220 --> 00:28:36,810
and asked him to do it.

721
00:28:37,130 --> 00:28:38,770
We used Xiuyu's name.

722
00:28:39,980 --> 00:28:40,740
So

723
00:28:41,770 --> 00:28:43,050
people outside all call Chuanmei

724
00:28:43,810 --> 00:28:46,420
Wang Xiuyu.

725
00:28:46,850 --> 00:28:47,660
Now,

726
00:28:49,290 --> 00:28:50,900
the Wangs got hold of this.

727
00:29:06,570 --> 00:29:09,220
How dare you?

728
00:29:10,260 --> 00:29:11,700
I'll hit you to death.

729
00:29:11,700 --> 00:29:12,130
Dad.

730
00:29:12,180 --> 00:29:13,330
You're irresponsible!

731
00:29:13,570 --> 00:29:15,180
Immoral!

732
00:29:15,530 --> 00:29:16,700
-I'll hit you.
-Dad, stop hitting Chuanjia.

733
00:29:16,700 --> 00:29:17,660
Bold, aren't you?

734
00:29:17,900 --> 00:29:18,660
Very bold.

735
00:29:18,900 --> 00:29:19,740
Don't touch me.

736
00:29:19,740 --> 00:29:20,810
I will hit you to death.

737
00:29:21,610 --> 00:29:23,740
-Why did you do that?
-Stop hitting him.

738
00:29:24,330 --> 00:29:25,980
How could you do that?

739
00:29:26,980 --> 00:29:28,810
Dad, what happened has happened.

740
00:29:28,810 --> 00:29:30,050
Chuanmei has graduated

741
00:29:30,050 --> 00:29:31,220
and has started working for a few years.

742
00:29:31,220 --> 00:29:32,290
What else can we do?

743
00:29:32,290 --> 00:29:35,050
You sure are fearless.

744
00:29:35,610 --> 00:29:38,180
Do you guys even respect the laws?

745
00:29:38,980 --> 00:29:41,180
Why would you do this?

746
00:29:41,180 --> 00:29:42,050
Who did I do this for?

747
00:29:42,290 --> 00:29:43,290
For Chuanmei.

748
00:29:43,290 --> 00:29:44,460
And for you.

749
00:29:44,900 --> 00:29:45,810
Back then,

750
00:29:45,810 --> 00:29:46,610
your biggest wish

751
00:29:46,610 --> 00:29:48,220
was for Chuanmei to get into a good university.

752
00:29:48,330 --> 00:29:49,700
When Chuanmei received the acceptance letter,

753
00:29:49,740 --> 00:29:51,130
you were over the moon.

754
00:29:51,130 --> 00:29:52,570
You were so happy.

755
00:29:52,570 --> 00:29:53,370
I have never seen you

756
00:29:53,370 --> 00:29:54,700
that happy before.

757
00:29:54,700 --> 00:29:55,330
Dad!

758
00:29:55,330 --> 00:29:56,500
Are you my father now?

759
00:29:56,500 --> 00:29:57,420
Shut up now.

760
00:29:57,420 --> 00:29:59,220
Or else, I'll slap you until you're a mute.

761
00:29:59,220 --> 00:30:00,370
Dad!

762
00:30:00,530 --> 00:30:02,810
What should we do
now that the Wangs know about it?

763
00:30:04,530 --> 00:30:05,570
What should we do?

764
00:30:08,260 --> 00:30:08,810
You...

765
00:30:09,770 --> 00:30:11,770
You two grew insolent.

766
00:30:11,770 --> 00:30:13,740
How could you do such a thing?

767
00:30:14,090 --> 00:30:15,980
She got accepted into the university.

768
00:30:16,220 --> 00:30:19,260
Why took her spot?

769
00:30:19,740 --> 00:30:21,220
This is her life.

770
00:30:21,220 --> 00:30:23,370
You ruined her life.

771
00:30:23,370 --> 00:30:24,420
Where's your good conscience?

772
00:30:24,850 --> 00:30:27,020
Where is it?

773
00:30:27,020 --> 00:30:27,850
Dad.

774
00:30:27,850 --> 00:30:29,370
This is not Chuanjia's fault.

775
00:30:29,370 --> 00:30:30,810
I implored Chuanjia to help me

776
00:30:30,810 --> 00:30:31,700
to get into a university.

777
00:30:31,700 --> 00:30:33,610
Chuanjia just wanted to help me.

778
00:30:33,610 --> 00:30:34,770
No, Dad.

779
00:30:34,770 --> 00:30:35,660
It's my fault.

780
00:30:35,660 --> 00:30:36,420
Blame me.

781
00:30:36,700 --> 00:30:38,220
I came up with the idea.

782
00:30:38,260 --> 00:30:39,220
Dad,

783
00:30:39,220 --> 00:30:39,980
I beg of you.

784
00:30:39,980 --> 00:30:40,980
Please help her.

785
00:30:40,980 --> 00:30:42,260
Help Chuanmei, okay?

786
00:30:44,740 --> 00:30:46,850
Dad, if this scandal breaks out,

787
00:30:46,850 --> 00:30:47,810
my life is over.

788
00:30:48,020 --> 00:30:49,220
I would rather die.

789
00:30:49,220 --> 00:30:51,370
There would be no point to live on.

790
00:31:00,500 --> 00:31:01,330
Chuanmei.

791
00:31:02,260 --> 00:31:03,020
For this thing,

792
00:31:03,740 --> 00:31:04,740
we're in the wrong.

793
00:31:05,420 --> 00:31:07,370
We made a huge mistake.

794
00:31:07,370 --> 00:31:08,900
This is evil.

795
00:31:08,900 --> 00:31:10,370
This is inhumane.

796
00:31:11,260 --> 00:31:12,220
Listen to me.

797
00:31:12,530 --> 00:31:13,460
Go visit the Wangs with me.

798
00:31:13,460 --> 00:31:14,980
We'll apologize to them with gifts.

799
00:31:15,260 --> 00:31:17,020
They'll decide what to make of you.

800
00:31:17,050 --> 00:31:18,850
They will hand you your punishment.

801
00:31:19,610 --> 00:31:20,370
And you.

802
00:31:20,570 --> 00:31:21,260
Quit your job.

803
00:31:21,460 --> 00:31:22,420
Come back.

804
00:31:22,740 --> 00:31:23,610
Forget your diploma.

805
00:31:23,610 --> 00:31:24,900
Forget your work.

806
00:31:25,130 --> 00:31:25,900
Come back.

807
00:31:25,900 --> 00:31:27,740
Work in Wanjia Group if you want.

808
00:31:27,740 --> 00:31:28,460
If you don't,

809
00:31:28,460 --> 00:31:29,420
stay home.

810
00:31:29,420 --> 00:31:31,090
I can support you.

811
00:31:31,370 --> 00:31:32,220
Chuanmei.

812
00:31:34,260 --> 00:31:34,980
My daughter.

813
00:31:35,330 --> 00:31:36,290
No!

814
00:31:36,850 --> 00:31:38,260
No one can know this.

815
00:31:38,810 --> 00:31:40,850
If everyone knows this,
how am I supposed to live?

816
00:31:41,500 --> 00:31:42,180
Also,

817
00:31:42,570 --> 00:31:44,130
did I come back this time

818
00:31:44,130 --> 00:31:45,050
just because I want everyone

819
00:31:45,050 --> 00:31:46,810
in the village to know I took Wang Xiuyu's spot?

820
00:31:47,050 --> 00:31:47,530
But...

821
00:31:48,260 --> 00:31:50,020
No one can know about this.

822
00:31:50,130 --> 00:31:52,330
What will she think of us?

823
00:31:52,330 --> 00:31:53,810
How can I live with dignity?

824
00:31:55,460 --> 00:31:56,180
No!

825
00:31:57,180 --> 00:31:57,980
I don't accept this.

826
00:31:58,850 --> 00:31:59,810
If you force me,

827
00:31:59,940 --> 00:32:01,020
I'll die in front of you.

828
00:32:01,020 --> 00:32:02,460
I'll join my mom.

829
00:32:02,700 --> 00:32:03,260
How dare you!

830
00:32:03,260 --> 00:32:04,770
I will join Mom!

831
00:32:05,020 --> 00:32:06,610
And you're threatening me with your mom?

832
00:32:06,940 --> 00:32:08,180
Even if you die now,

833
00:32:08,370 --> 00:32:09,290
your mom

834
00:32:09,420 --> 00:32:11,420
will reject you in the afterlife.

835
00:32:11,460 --> 00:32:12,900
Dad.

836
00:32:12,980 --> 00:32:13,420
Calm down.

837
00:32:13,420 --> 00:32:14,090
Take it out on me.

838
00:32:14,090 --> 00:32:15,460
Just take it out on me.

839
00:32:16,180 --> 00:32:16,700
You know what?

840
00:32:16,810 --> 00:32:17,330
What about this?

841
00:32:17,500 --> 00:32:18,180
From now on,

842
00:32:18,460 --> 00:32:20,740
you don't need to provide for me.
I'll be on my own.

843
00:32:21,740 --> 00:32:22,810
Dad, I'm begging you.

844
00:32:22,810 --> 00:32:24,370
I have never begged you.

845
00:32:24,810 --> 00:32:26,090
Just this once,

846
00:32:26,090 --> 00:32:27,460
please help Chuanmei.

847
00:32:27,460 --> 00:32:28,770
Help her.

848
00:32:28,770 --> 00:32:30,260
You should help me.

849
00:32:30,500 --> 00:32:31,660
Oh, for heaven's sake.

850
00:32:35,090 --> 00:32:35,610
Dad.

851
00:32:36,260 --> 00:32:36,770
Dad.

852
00:32:39,810 --> 00:32:41,050
[Medical Area]
Hang in there, Mr. Wu.

853
00:32:41,370 --> 00:32:42,330
We're in the hospital now.

854
00:32:43,180 --> 00:32:43,700
How are you feeling?

855
00:32:43,940 --> 00:32:44,740
Are you all right?

856
00:32:44,940 --> 00:32:45,770
Okay, I guess.

857
00:32:46,460 --> 00:32:47,330
Xingfu,

858
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:48,980
the omen has come true.

859
00:32:49,420 --> 00:32:50,500
The omen has come true.

860
00:32:51,140 --> 00:32:52,070
Please don't joke around.

861
00:32:52,470 --> 00:32:53,230
Is it very serious?

862
00:32:54,030 --> 00:32:56,230
Then I'll get a number for you now.

863
00:32:56,420 --> 00:32:57,230
Xingfu.

864
00:32:57,750 --> 00:32:58,510
Why are you here?

865
00:32:58,660 --> 00:32:59,270
Did something happen?

866
00:33:00,070 --> 00:33:01,710
One client fell from the mountain.

867
00:33:02,470 --> 00:33:03,310
Is it serious?

868
00:33:03,950 --> 00:33:04,950
Very!

869
00:33:05,710 --> 00:33:06,380
Well.

870
00:33:06,550 --> 00:33:07,420
Come back.

871
00:33:07,990 --> 00:33:09,990
Bring him to Room 3.

872
00:33:09,990 --> 00:33:11,900
I'll ask Mr. Zhou to look at him right away.

873
00:33:12,750 --> 00:33:13,660
Go now!

874
00:33:13,820 --> 00:33:15,140
Place him there now.

875
00:33:15,204 --> 00:33:19,600
[Outpatient]

876
00:33:25,550 --> 00:33:27,550
This is too serious.

877
00:33:28,790 --> 00:33:29,950
It's crazy.

878
00:33:30,340 --> 00:33:31,750
We need to think it through.

879
00:33:36,550 --> 00:33:37,750
If this went out,

880
00:33:38,140 --> 00:33:39,470
both our family and Mr. Wan

881
00:33:39,990 --> 00:33:41,310
would be done for.

882
00:33:41,550 --> 00:33:42,070
Mom,

883
00:33:43,660 --> 00:33:46,340
Xiuyu is the victim here.

884
00:33:47,270 --> 00:33:48,860
Why are you defending someone else's interest?

885
00:33:49,140 --> 00:33:50,660
I'm not defending their interest.

886
00:33:50,660 --> 00:33:51,310
I...

887
00:33:51,310 --> 00:33:51,580
I'm thinking

888
00:33:51,580 --> 00:33:52,900
for us.

